Launched on September 27, 2024, Birla Ojasvi is designed by the renowned global architectural firm Broadway Malyan. It offers a host of premium amenities, including two clubhouses with 50+ facilities, a 350-ft tall sky club with panoramic city views on the 33rd floor of Tower 1 (Signature Tower), and ample open spaces to ensure a refreshing lifestyle. The township overlooks the serene 250-acre Turahalli reserve forest, enhancing the connection with nature.

Tower 1 (Signature Tower) houses 121 exclusive 3 BHK signature apartments with only 4 units per floor. Towers 2 and 3 accommodate 248 and 238 units, respectively, with a mix of 1, 2, and 3 BHK apartments. The project maintains strict adherence to quality and sustainability standards, reflected in its high RERA rating (9.2/10) and official RERA registration (PRM/KA/RERA/1251/310/PR/040924/006989).

Prices range from Rs 68 Lakhs for 1 BHK units (sold out) to Rs 5.25 Crores for 4 BHK row houses. Construction began in January 2025, with possession expected by January 2031. Birla Ojasvi promises a premium lifestyle combining luxury, connectivity, and nature in one of Bangalore‚Äôs fastest-growing residential hubs.',
