    'Magnolia Delight',
    'Magnolia Delight',
    'Magnolia Delight by Magnolia Infrastructure Development Limited is a prestigious residential project nestled in the prime location of R.T. Nagar, Bengaluru. This exclusive development comprises just 48 ultra-spacious 3 BHK luxury apartments set amidst lush landscaped gardens and open spaces that cover 70% of the 0.88-acre land. The project boasts a single tower with ground plus 13 floors, thoughtfully crafted to offer a serene yet sophisticated urban lifestyle.

Designed with architectural excellence and vastu-compliance, each apartment in Magnolia Delight offers expansive living areas with cross ventilation, ensuring abundant natural light and healthy airflow. Apartment sizes range between 2480 to 2668 sq.ft, featuring well-planned layouts including formal living rooms, integrated or separate dining spaces, servant rooms, utility areas, and multiple balconies that overlook beautiful courtyards and garden retreats. High-quality materials like premium marble flooring in living and dining areas and wooden flooring in master bedrooms enhance the luxurious ambiance.

Residents enjoy a rich array of amenities including a temperature-controlled infinity pool with a children‚Äôs pool, state-of-the-art fitness center, rooftop gardens, horizon yoga deck, clubhouse, business center, recreation rooms featuring indoor games like billiards and table tennis, a multipurpose ballroom, and open-air gala spaces designed for social events. The premises ensure uncompromising safety with 24/7 surveillance, metal detectors, firefighting systems, and concierge services.

Magnolia Delight‚Äôs strategic location offers seamless connectivity to key commercial and IT hubs such as Manyata Tech Park, Nagavara, Hebbal, and the Outer Ring Road. It‚Äôs close to reputed educational institutions, super specialty hospitals, malls like Orion and Elements, entertainment zones, and benefits from proximity to the upcoming Namma Metro and Kempegowda International Airport.

