    'Purva Silver Sky',
    'Purva Silver Sky is a premium residential project by Puravankara Group in Hebbagodi, near Electronic City Phase 2, Bangalore. Launched in December 2025, it spans 7-7.5 acres with 3 towers (up to G+30/32 floors) offering 350-356 luxury units in 3, 3.5, 4, and penthouse configurations.
