    'VPROJ030625-113714-1493',
    'Brigade Laguna',
    'Brigade Laguna',
    'Brigade Laguna is a premium lakeside residential project by Brigade Group, located at Rachenahalli, near Hebbal in North Bangalore. Nestled beside the scenic Rachenahalli Lake, this thoughtfully planned development offers a tranquil lifestyle with high-end urban conveniences and exceptional connectivity to key parts of the city.

